Package: scryptoC
Type: Package
Title: Crypto Currency Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sree Latha", "Vallabhaneni", email = "vallabhaneni.sreelatha@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: This package looks at Crypto currency as a printed data for the present status of leading currencies.
    Extract, clean and loads one year data of Bitcoin, Ethereum, XRP from coinmarketcap.
    Plot the variables available for the chosen currency with respect to time.
    Fit the data for chosen currency and selected variable out of Closing price and Market Cap using smooth.spline model.
    Plots the fit data of the chosen currency and variable.
